title: #94: Sex: Take It Or Leave It (Dov Davidoff)
itunes:title: Sex: Take It Or Leave It with Dov Davidoff
description: Dov Davidoff came over to my pig sty to talk to me about his overactive libido. He's pretty adamant that it's not an addiction. So I'd say it's more of a compulsion. Anyway, it was a fun conversation. Join us.
